  Author                   = {I Manai and A Molineri and C Fr{\'{e}}javille and C Duval and P Bataille and R Journet and F Wiotte and B Laburthe-Tolra and E Mar{\'{e}}chal and M Cheneau and M {Robert-de-Saint-Vincent}},
